1. Introduction

These Terms and Conditions govern your use of AUTOBOLI LTD’s services, including the subscription to auction data services provided via our website. By signing up for our services, you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms.

2. Eligibility

AUTOBOLI LTD offers subscription-based access to auction data collected across the UK. Subscribers receive full access to all available data with no tiered restrictions.

AUTOBOLI LTD is exclusively designed for use by independent dealers, motor dealers, traders, and individuals engaged in the motor business. By using our platform, you confirm that you meet this criterion. We reserve the right to terminate or suspend accounts if we determine that a user does not meet these eligibility requirements.

Use of the Platform

Users may only access, browse, and utilize the platform to gather information related to auctions for professional purposes within the motor business industry. Unauthorized use, including for personal or non-business purposes, is strictly prohibited.

3. Data Accuracy

Our platform aggregates vehicle auction data from third-party sources. While we strive for accuracy and comprehensiveness, all information is provided “as-is.” AUTOBOLI LTD does not guarantee the reliability, availability, or correctness of the data and is not liable for decisions made based on this information. Read disclaimer

4. Subscriptions and Billing

Subscription Start Date: Your subscription will begin on the day you sign up. If your subscription starts after the 1st of any month, you will be charged a prorated amount for the remaining days of that month.

Billing Cycle: Following the initial prorated charge, subsequent payments will be collected via direct debit on the 1st of each month.

Payment Method: By subscribing, you authorize AUTOBOLI LTD to charge the agreed-upon subscription fee through your provided payment method.

Restrictions

Users are prohibited from:

  • Sharing access to their account with unauthorized persons.
  • Redistributing, copying, or modifying data from the platform.
  • Using the platform for non-business or personal purposes unrelated to the motor business.

Pricing

Subscription prices are listed on our website and may be subject to change. Any changes to pricing will be communicated in advance and take effect in the next billing cycle.

5. Cancellations and Refunds

You can cancel your subscription at any time. Cancellations will be effective at the end of the current billing cycle. You will continue to have access to our services until the subscription period ends.

  • Refunds are not provided for partially used months or for any unused services.

6. Intellectual Property

All content, branding, and design on the AUTOBOLI LTD platform are the intellectual property of AUTOBOLI LTD and may not be reproduced or used without prior written consent.

7. Termination of Service

Subscribers are permitted to use the auction data provided for internal business purposes only. Redistribution or sharing of the data with third parties is prohibited without express written consent from AUTOBOLI LTD.

AUTOBOLI LTD reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts for misuse, failure to comply with these terms, or any action that compromises the integrity of our services or data.

Upon termination, you will no longer have access to the auction data and will not be entitled to any refunds for the remaining period of your subscription.

8. Privacy Policy

Please refer to our Privacy Policy for details on how we collect, store, and use your data. Click here

9. Disclaimer of Liability

AUTOBOLI LTD is an aggregator of auction data and does not own or control the information provided. We disclaim liability for the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of third-party data. Users are encouraged to verify all details with original sources. Read more

To the fullest extent permitted by law, AUTOBOLI LTD will not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services.

10. Changes to Terms

AUTOBOLI LTD reserves the right to modify these Terms and Conditions at any time. We will notify you of any changes, and your continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.

11. Contact Information

If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us.
